title: Fraternity Vacation 80`s(DVD, 2002)
description:
Movie Description
Two frat animals, saddled with a nerdy "brother" on a pleasure trip to Palm Springs, bet a rival that they can be the first to "score" with an aloof blonde.

Credits 
Cast: Stephen Geoffreys 
Director: James Frawley 

Synopsis
A group of fraternity brothers leave behind their snowy Iowa digs for the sunny -- and scantily-clad -- sights of Palm Springs, California.

When they arrive, the boys meet a curvaceous blonde named Ashley Taylor, and immediately step in each other&#039;s way to bed her first.

But the geek among these self-styled studs, Wendall Tvedt, has a surprise for all concerned...

Industry Reviews
"...[The filmmakers] are well served by a decent young cast....The numerous pop tunes, including three from Bananarama, are all bouncy..."
Cart.
